```scala
class Buffer {
  def f[@specialized(Int) T](): T = 0 match {
    case 0 => 0.asInstanceOf[T]
    case 1 => 0.asInstanceOf[T]
  }
}
```

causes stack overflow in 2.10.0

```
uncaught exception during compilation: java.lang.StackOverflowError
